---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Astro SEO Blog — our mission to share practical SEO and content strategy insights for modern web developers and marketers."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__lead">
        We help developers, marketers, and business owners build websites that rank,
        convert, and perform.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Astro SEO Blog was founded on a simple belief: great SEO shouldn't require
          expensive agencies or black-hat tactics. With the right knowledge and tools,
          anyone can build a sustainable organic growth engine.
        </p>
        <p>
          We publish in-depth guides on on-page optimization, content strategy, technical
          SEO, and modern web development—always with a focus on actionable advice you
          can implement today.
        </p>

        <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Practical over theoretical</strong> — Every article includes steps you can follow immediately.</li>
          <li><strong>Modern stack focus</strong> — We specialize in static sites, Astro, and Jamstack architectures.</li>
          <li><strong>Data-driven</strong> — Our recommendations are backed by current search engine guidelines and real-world results.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Team</h2>
        <p>
          Our contributors are SEO specialists, content strategists, and full-stack developers
          with years of experience helping businesses grow through organic search. We practice
          what we preach—this very site is built with Astro and optimized using the same
          techniques we write about.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
